.. [#at] The RS485 circuit controls the Input and Output direction automatically, thereâ€™s no need to control it from within the software.

.. [#wi] The default product without the CM5 does not include a Wi-Fi/BT module. You can include a CM5 that has the Wi-Fi/BT module at the Chipsee store during the ordering process.

